<td align="left" valign="top">
<p><br><br>

Dear Parent or Guardian of {!Contact.Name},<BR><BR>

Thank you for submitting {!Contact.FirstName}’s application to take part in NCS (National Citizen Service) this autumn.<BR><BR> We wanted to let you know that we have received your application and are processing it.<br><BR>

We will call you as we get closer to the programme start date to gather further details about the medical and support information you gave us about {!Contact.FirstName}. This is so we can get an up-to-date understanding of any staff support or logistical adjustments {!Contact.FirstName} might need on the programme.
<BR><BR>
In the meantime, you can visit our <a href="http://questions.ncsthechallenge.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; color: #eb008b;"><strong>Questions page</strong></a> which contains lots of useful information about our programme. Or, if you would like to get in touch with us directly, please email us at <b>contact@ncsthechallenge.org</b> or call <b>0203 542 2400</b>.<BR><BR>

Don't forget, we have NCS programmes running throughout this summer. If {!Contact.FirstName} is able to take part in NCS this summer, please log in to our website and add the dates they can attend as there may be a chance {!Contact.FirstName} could still get a place. Alternatively, you can give us a call on the number above to discuss this.<br><br>

Yours sincerely,
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px;"><img alt="Tanya Dunne" border="0" height="61" src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/CCT/Tanya%20Dunne.png?height=30&amp;width=122" width="122"></p>
Tanya Dunne<BR>
Head of Customer Services - The Challenge</P>

